<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 16:08:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>辛贝特起诉以色列人，据称该人被伊朗在网上招募从事反国家行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-to-indict-israeli-allegedly-recruited-by-iran-to-commit-acts-against-state/00000190-bbd9-d211-a5da-ffdbe2140000</link><description>21 岁的 Elimelech Stern 是以色列中部城市贝特谢梅什的居民，据称伊朗情报部门在网上联系并要求他执行悬挂横幅、藏匿金钱和运送包裹等“任务”，以换取报酬，随后被捕。加密货币支付</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:52:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-to-indict-israeli-allegedly-recruited-by-iran-to-commit-acts-against-state/00000190-bbd9-d211-a5da-ffdbe2140000</guid></item><item><title>一场巨大的欺诈使以色列数亿美元的养老金被抹去。国家什么都不做</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-huge-fraud-erased-hundreds-of-millions-of-israeli-pensions-the-state-wont-protect-them/00000190-bb65-db47-abb0-bb7556920001</link><description>资本市场管理局承认，近一年来，在其监管下的养老金中，有数亿谢克尔被盗，但没有一个受害者被告知。但接受指责是另一回事</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-huge-fraud-erased-hundreds-of-millions-of-israeli-pensions-the-state-wont-protect-them/00000190-bb65-db47-abb0-bb7556920001</guid></item><item><title>以色列公设辩护律师：战时紧急立法严重侵犯囚犯权利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/public-defender-emergency-legislation-during-the-war-infringes-on-rights-of-prisoners/00000190-bb73-de8b-adfc-bb73ea3c0000</link><description>根据公设辩护人办公室 2023 年活动报告，自以色列与加沙哈马斯战争爆发以来，提起的恐怖主义煽动起诉数量比过去四年还要多，同时对警察暴行的投诉也激增</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:06:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/public-defender-emergency-legislation-during-the-war-infringes-on-rights-of-prisoners/00000190-bb73-de8b-adfc-bb73ea3c0000</guid></item><item><title>数万名阿拉伯人住在耶路撒冷，没有自来水：“它将成为第二个加沙”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-arabs-living-in-jerusalem-without-running-water-it-will-become-a-second-gaza/00000190-bb83-db81-a3f7-fb9fe9680000</link><description>耶路撒冷最大的城区缺乏自来水，似乎没有人关心：Kafr Aqab 的居民每周只能获得几个小时的水，无法洗衣服或洗地板，被迫放弃淋浴</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 14:09:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-arabs-living-in-jerusalem-without-running-water-it-will-become-a-second-gaza/00000190-bb83-db81-a3f7-fb9fe9680000</guid></item><item><title>位智前首席执行官：“如果我们采取正确的步骤，新加坡将像我们旁边的加沙一样”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-we-take-the-right-steps-singapore-will-look-like-gaza-next-to-us/00000190-b1bc-df47-a7bf-b1be45b20000</link><description>以色列科技界最成功的人物之一诺姆·巴丁 (Noam Bardin) 在美国工作 13 年后于 10 月 7 日后的第二天返回以色列。“这场巨大的危机为这个国家提供了一个‘重启’的机会，尽管代价高昂。” ，”他告诉《国土报》</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 13:47:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-we-take-the-right-steps-singapore-will-look-like-gaza-next-to-us/00000190-b1bc-df47-a7bf-b1be45b20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军告诉高等法院：许多坦克在战争中受损，弹药短缺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-tells-high-court-many-tanks-damaged-in-the-war-there-is-ashortage-in-ammunition/00000190-bb29-de8b-adfc-bb298b860000</link><description>针对女兵要求被允许在战斗岗位服役的请愿书，以色列军队回复称，由于战争，将推迟将女性编入装甲部队，该计划将于 2025 年 11 月启动</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 12:15:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-tells-high-court-many-tanks-damaged-in-the-war-there-is-ashortage-in-ammunition/00000190-bb29-de8b-adfc-bb298b860000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：如果没有以色列，世界上每个犹太人都将面临危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/biden-without-israel-every-jew-in-the-world-would-be-at-risk/00000190-bac9-d458-a3d7-bbefa3f00000</link><description>拜登加强了对以色列的立场，称自己是犹太复国主义者。 “你不必是犹太人才能成为犹太复国主义者，”他在周一的采访中说。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:22:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/biden-without-israel-every-jew-in-the-world-would-be-at-risk/00000190-bac9-d458-a3d7-bbefa3f00000</guid></item><item><title>有一段时间，加沙人希望战争能够结束。现在他们感觉自己被抛弃了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/for-a-moment-gazans-had-hope-the-war-would-end-now-they-feel-theyve-been-abandoned/00000190-bab2-d211-a5da-fffb31440000</link><description>加沙人民说，世界只关心穆罕默德·德伊夫发生了什么，“没有人再谈论数十名死者了”。一位人权活动人士表示，过去曾有国际压力，但“现在，每个人都在等待内塔尼亚胡”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:02:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/for-a-moment-gazans-had-hope-the-war-would-end-now-they-feel-theyve-been-abandoned/00000190-bab2-d211-a5da-fffb31440000</guid></item><item><title>阻止向加沙提供援助的极右团体获得美国和以色列的免税捐款</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/far-right-groups-blocking-aid-to-gaza-receive-tax-deductible-donations-from-us-and-israel/00000190-ba8f-db47-abb0-baffc7370000</link><description>尽管受到制裁，三个极端民族主义团体仍从美国和以色列收到了超过 20 万美元的免税捐款。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 09:06:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/far-right-groups-blocking-aid-to-gaza-receive-tax-deductible-donations-from-us-and-israel/00000190-ba8f-db47-abb0-baffc7370000</guid></item><item><title>人质交易的框架仍然存在。细节等待以色列领导人的意见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/a-framework-for-a-hostage-deal-still-exists-the-details-await-israels-leaders-input/00000190-ba57-d458-a3d7-bbf7ad6a0000</link><description>现在重要的问题不是哈马斯领导人穆罕默德·德伊夫是生还是死，而是谈判将会发生什么。僵局可能会持续到美国大选，从而进一步危及人质的生命安全，并大大增加以色列和黎巴嫩之间爆发全面战争的可能性</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 08:49:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/a-framework-for-a-hostage-deal-still-exists-the-details-await-israels-leaders-input/00000190-ba57-d458-a3d7-bbf7ad6a0000</guid></item><item><title>三名军官和一名哲学家：决定谁是依良心拒服兵役者的秘密以色列国防军委员会内部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/three-officers-and-a-philosopher-inside-the-secretive-idf-conscience-committee/00000190-b619-df08-a9fe-f7d9b7c10000</link><description>人权倡导者表示，根据以色列国防军对该术语的定义，即使是马丁·路德·金和圣雄甘地也不会被视为良心拒服兵役者。委员会中的学者、活动人士、反对者和律师告诉《国土报》，军事系统如何应对挑衅的拒绝者</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 06:12:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/three-officers-and-a-philosopher-inside-the-secretive-idf-conscience-committee/00000190-b619-df08-a9fe-f7d9b7c10000</guid></item><item><title>美国犹太艺术家对美化哈马斯大屠杀的艺术作品感到愤怒，感到沉默和疏远</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-jewish-artists-angered-by-artwork-that-glorifies-hamas-massacre-feel-alienated/00000190-b011-d7ee-af9c-ff1925b20000</link><description>当纽约一个著名的文化空间向一位艺术家展示其橱窗并对哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击表示赞赏时，许多犹太和以色列艺术家感到震惊，但并不完全感到惊讶。正如一位策展人所指责的那样，艺术界是否创造了“一个从单一角度看待现实的平坦领域”？</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:35:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-jewish-artists-angered-by-artwork-that-glorifies-hamas-massacre-feel-alienated/00000190-b011-d7ee-af9c-ff1925b20000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡命令以色列军队在10月7日之后关闭会议录音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ordered-israeli-army-to-turn-off-recording-of-meetings-after-october-7/00000190-b7ef-db47-abb0-bfffd0900000</link><description>通常情况下，录音系统是自动运行的，记录陆军总部指挥中心发生的一切，但战争一开始，总理就下令关闭所有录音。军队遵守了这个命令</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 03:02:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ordered-israeli-army-to-turn-off-recording-of-meetings-after-october-7/00000190-b7ef-db47-abb0-bfffd0900000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙作战，10 月 7 日炮击基布兹房屋的以色列国防军坦克军官表示“我别无选择”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/now-fighting-in-gaza-idf-officer-who-shelled-a-kibbutz-house-on-october-7-has-no-regrets/00000190-b806-db47-abb0-ba77d8b20000</link><description>10月7日，尼西姆·哈赞上校控制了一辆受损的坦克，并将其开往贝埃里基布兹，在那里他与哈马斯恐怖分子进行了整整两天的战斗。正是在那里，他向佩西·科恩的家发射了一枚炮弹。他告诉《国土报》，他不知道里面有人质。 “那天我们需要改变现状，”他说</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 03:01:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/now-fighting-in-gaza-idf-officer-who-shelled-a-kibbutz-house-on-october-7-has-no-regrets/00000190-b806-db47-abb0-ba77d8b20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称其杀死了哈马斯一半的军事领导层，14,000名成员死伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-live/barrage-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-after-three-killed-in-lebanon-airstrike/00000190-b936-db47-abb0-bb77e2b30000</link><description>哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部称，昨天有 49 名巴勒斯坦人在加沙地带丧生 ■ 加沙边境社区启动火箭警报 ■ 以色列人因涉嫌与伊朗情报部门接触而被捕 ■ 巴勒斯坦报道：以色列国防军与巴拉塔难民营武装分子交火, 约旦河西岸 ■ 以色列边境警察在约旦河西岸持刀袭击中受轻伤</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 02:33:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-live/barrage-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-after-three-killed-in-lebanon-airstrike/00000190-b936-db47-abb0-bb77e2b30000</guid></item><item><title>JD万斯在当选特朗普副总统后首次发表讲话，敦促以色列“尽快”结束加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/j-d-vance-trumps-vp-pick-urges-israel-to-finish-gaza-war-as-quick-as-possible/00000190-b947-da51-a19a-fdef7b240000</link><description>这位俄亥俄州参议员曾写道，特朗普可能是“美国的希特勒”，他指责拜登总统“让以色列越来越难赢得这场战争”，并发誓要“重振以色列和沙特阿拉伯之间的和平进程”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 02:24:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/j-d-vance-trumps-vp-pick-urges-israel-to-finish-gaza-war-as-quick-as-possible/00000190-b947-da51-a19a-fdef7b240000</guid></item><item><title>报道：国防部长加兰特告诉人质家属“以色列有史以来最接近达成协议”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-this-is-the-closest-we-have-ever-been-to-a-deal/00000190-b7e9-db81-a3f7-f7fda3ae0000</link><description>据以色列第 12 频道援引未透露姓名的消息人士的报道，10 月 7 日，国防部长约夫·加兰特在会见在军事基地被绑架的以色列国防军女观察员家属时，暗示与哈马斯的人质谈判取得了重大进展</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:58:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-this-is-the-closest-we-have-ever-been-to-a-deal/00000190-b7e9-db81-a3f7-f7fda3ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院命令国家解释为什么斯德泰曼拘留设施不依法运作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-state-explain-why-sde-teiman-doesnt-operate-according-to-the-law/00000190-b7b6-db47-abb0-bff71d060000</link><description>该国表示打算将被拘留者转移到以色列其他监狱或将他们送回加沙，但此后一再要求推迟。在该州再次要求推迟后，法官要求政府在 10 天内做出回应</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:45:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-state-explain-why-sde-teiman-doesnt-operate-according-to-the-law/00000190-b7b6-db47-abb0-bff71d060000</guid></item><item><title>2014年，以色列与哈马斯开战。十年后，我们正经历着残酷的重演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/in-2014-israel-went-to-war-with-hamas-ten-years-later-we-are-living-a-grim-replay/00000190-b777-d5a5-af99-ff7794060000</link><description>我们已经用十年的时间从​​ 2014 年发生的事件中汲取教训，其中许多事件似乎预示着即将发生的事情。这一次，没有任何借口让加沙恢复现状——我们已经看到，这对于以色列人和巴勒斯坦人来说是多么不可持续和危险</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:43:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/in-2014-israel-went-to-war-with-hamas-ten-years-later-we-are-living-a-grim-replay/00000190-b777-d5a5-af99-ff7794060000</guid></item><item><title>以色列消息人士称，试图杀死德伊夫损害了与哈马斯的停火谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/attempt-to-kill-deif-hurt-cease-fire-negotiations-with-hamas-israeli-sources-say/00000190-b792-db47-abb0-bff3bcd40000</link><description>一位以色列消息人士表示，“事情并没有像往常一样进行。”一位政府消息人士称，“哈马斯遭受了严重打击，他们对这一事件的反应非常软弱，近乎无反应。”结果，摩萨德主任尚未启程前往卡塔尔进行谈判</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:39:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/attempt-to-kill-deif-hurt-cease-fire-negotiations-with-hamas-israeli-sources-say/00000190-b792-db47-abb0-bff3bcd40000</guid></item></channel></rss>